'''''Encyclopedia of American Religions''''', renamed '''''Melton's Encyclopedia of American Religions''''' in the eighth edition, is a reference book by [[J. Gordon Melton]] first published in 1978, by Consortium Books, A McGrath publishing company. It is currently in its ninth edition and has become a standard reference work in the study of [[religion in the United States]].<ref>{{cite journal |last=Lippy |first=Charles H. |title=The Encyclopedia of American Religions second edition supplement |journal=[[Journal of American History]] |volume=75 |issue=4 |date=March 1989 |pages=1401 |doi=10.2307/1908781 |publisher=Organization of American Historians |last2=Melton |first2=J. Gordon |jstor=1908781}}</ref>

